      "releaseNotes": "Q: Why couldn't the string quartet find their composer? \nA: He was Haydn.\n\n::Takes a bow::\n\nThis update fixes the analyze mini-player not showing the buttons correctly.\n\nAs always, if you like this update, please leave a kind rating and review. It helps more than you know. Thanks!",
